e="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> the words <amend.in>of each unit trust, not being</amend.in>, and substituting the words <amend.in>, in relation to each unit trust, that is not</amend.in>:</text>
              </para>
            </label-para>
            <label-para skeleton="no" xml:lang="en-NZ">
