le="xx_XX" atidlm:state="UNCHANGED"/></atidlm:resourcepair></atidlm:link></citation> the words <amend.in>of each unit trust</amend.in>, and substituting the words <amend.in>, in relation to each unit trust</amend.in>.</text>
